re.com/it-industry-news/strategy/7061-tcs-acquires-it-consultancy-firm-for-a$15m |title=TCS acquires IT consultancy firm for A$15m |publisher=ITWire.com |date=12 November 2006 |accessdate=7 September 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131228062918/http://www.itwire.com/it-industry-news/strategy/7061-tcs-acquires-it-consultancy-firm-for-a$15m |archive-date=28 December 2013 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2006-11-08/news/27424804_1_australian-business-consulting-australian-dollars |title=TCS acquires Australian consultancy firm |newspaper=Economic Times |date=8 November 2006 |accessdate=7 September 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n| TKS-Teknosoft\n| 2006 November\n| Banking Product\n| {{flag|CH}}\n| $80.4 m\n| 115\n| Expand product portfolio by acquiring rights to Quartz and ownership of Alpha and e-portfolio, enhanced presence in Switzerland and France\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.financialexpress.com/news/tcs-acquires-swiss-firm-tksteknosoft/182435/|title=TCS acquires Swiss firm TKS-Teknosoft|publisher=Financial Express|date=1 November 2006 |accessdate=7 September 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n| Citigroup Global Services Limited\n| 2008 December\n| Captive BPO of [[Citigroup Inc.]]\n| {{flag|IND}}\n| $512 m\n| 12,472\n| TCS acquired key Banking and Financial Services (BFS) domain knowledge.\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=newsarchive&sid=aZ8HTV7QJlsA |title=Tata Consultancy Services to Acquire Citigroup Global Services |publisher=Bloomberg.com|date=8 October 2008|accessdate=8 September 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2008-10-09/news/28436872_1_cgsl-citigroup-global-services-tcs |title=TCS takes a lead, but deal raises a few concerns |newspaper=Economic Times |date=9 October 2008 |accessdate=8 September 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n| Supervalu Services India\n| 2010 September\n| Captive IT/BPO